    Class with convenience methods for transforming various tree data structures into plain Newick strings.
    NewickVertex
    Holds a "pure" multifurcating Newick vertex or tree, typically used only as an intermediate form after reading tree input before creating more specialised representations (bifurcating, ultrametric, non-node based, etc.).
    PrIMENewickTree
    Extension of a NewickTree which parses the PrIME-specific meta info and provides simplified access to such data (alongside the original topology).
